h3. Summary
The information given to create another issue from the Create Issue dialog is extremely vague.  This should be updated to be more specific.  In the 6.0 document it contained a list of fields which are not pre-populated - this is still the case, and perhaps some custom fields from third-party add-ons.  Users need some clarity on this functionality.  

