h3. Problem Definition
Currently, when a deactivated user tries to login into JIRA, it will prompt the following:
{code}
Sorry, your username and password are incorrect - please try again.
{code}
The above error message is not meaningful enough for them to know their account is being deactivated.
h3. Suggested Solution
It should prompt an error message which will allow them to send email to the JIRA local administrator for re-activation. Example:
{code}
Your account has been deactivated, please contact xxx@blah.com
{code}

